                  <p class="ia-table-text">• Option 0: ‘No change’ counterfactual.</p>
                  <p class="ia-table-text"><b>Option 1 (preferred)</b>: A package to reform the role of Companies House, including increasing the powers of the Registrar of Companies to query and remove information on the register, introducing identity verification for directors and people with significant control and changing requirements around filing of company accounts.</p>
                </td>
