          <num>85.</num>
          <content>
            <p>Therefore, we expect that costs arising from the changing of company names will be minimal as the power will primarily be exercised where there is an identified error, anomaly or inaccuracy which appears fraudulent, suspicious or may impact the integrity of the register or wider business environment.</p>
