        </paragraph>
        <paragraph>
          <num>421.</num>
          <content>
            <p>All Companies House Service developments take into account the needs of service users across the range of protected characteristics, and customer strategy currently makes arrangements for those in vulnerable groups. Companies House will continue to do so under these reforms. </p>
